title: Camp WeWow Shark Week Day 2
description:
It's Shark Week at Camp WeWow! Today, we're learning about shark buoyance!! Visit tinkercast.com/resource/experiment-how-in-the-wow-do-sharks-float-2 for directions to today's activity and share what you're tinkering with at tinkercast.com/share! Have you overcome a fear?! Call us at 1-888-7WOW-WOW to share how you learned to tackled one of your fears! You just might get featured around the Camp WeWow Campfire this Friday!
